安驻军密为保护，如何盼复。请令","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"5181c54f0c"},{"id":"d95683888c","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]指胡宗南、曾万钟、关麟征。电台时刻联络","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"5181c54f0c"},{"id":"93a60be1a8","type":"paragraph","text":"弟东来","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"5181c54f0c"},{"id":"b665f4dbcd","type":"paragraph","text":"元午","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"5181c54f0c"}],"page":{"id":"23999bf88c","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"5181c54f0c","start":158,"end":159}}}},"__N_SSG":true}